LTCRabbit,is,a,Litecoin,LTC,and,X,coin,mining,service,All,payouts,even,for,X,coins,are,in,LTC,and,users,can,earn,additional,LTC,through,the,LTCRabbit,affiliate,program,The,LTCRabbit,API,allows,users,to,retrieve,general,pool,information,user,earnings,information,and,shoutbox,messages,The,API,also,lets,users,create,and,delete,workers,and,post,messages,to,the,shoutbox